name: Kevin Sullivan
summary: Legendary professional wrestler Kevin Sullivan, known as "The Taskmaster," has passed away at the age of 74. Sullivan, who wrestled primarily for World Championship Wrestling (WCW), suffered a severe accident three months ago which ultimately led to his demise. Fellow wrestlers and the wrestling community have expressed their condolences and shared memories of Sullivan's contributions to the sport.

name: USA vs France basketball
summary: The 2024 Paris Olympics are set to showcase a captivating men's basketball gold medal game between Team USA and France. The two powerhouses will face off on August 8th, with coverage available on NBC Connecticut, CBS Sports, and other major news outlets. Team USA, the reigning gold medalists, will be looking to defend their title against a formidable French team that reached the finals by defeating Lithuania. The game promises to be a thrilling encounter, with experts predicting a potential "epic battle for gold." Despite being heavy favorites, Team USA will need to be at their best to overcome a talented French squad led by NBA star Rudy Gobert. The match-up is a rematch of the 2020 Tokyo Olympics final, where Team USA emerged victorious.

name: USA Basketball
summary: Team USA's women's basketball team aims to extend their Olympic gold medal streak to eight at the 2024 Paris Games. They face competition from seven other teams vying for the top spot. Despite their dominance, USA Basketball's presence at the Olympics has been scrutinized as an awkward fit due to its overwhelming superiority. The men's team is set to face Serbia in the semifinals and has advanced to the semifinals with a victory over Brazil. However, their path to a gold medal faces challenges, as evidenced by their narrow escape against Serbia where they overcame a 17-point deficit. The upcoming matchup against Serbia in the semifinals will be crucial for their bid to reach the final and contend for the gold medal against France.
